title: The Grad Club
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, Western, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Canadian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Not-for-profit inclusive pub/space for locals as well as Queen's University faculty and staff plus and students, established since 1963. Veg choices are denoted on the menu; some could be made vegan. Ask for vegan faux chicken strips in place of chicken. Offers a chickpea burger - vegans ask to omit mayonaise.
